      <title>保守党无法掩盖其在移民问题上的失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-06-05/uk-election-farage-shows-tories-can-t-hide-from-their-immigration-failures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守党坚持将移民问题作为竞选的核心议题，但其限制移民的目标却始终未能实现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-06-05/uk-election-farage-shows-tories-can-t-hide-from-their-immigration-failures</guid>
