      <title>普京旗舰论坛为俄罗斯精英子女提供舞台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/putin-s-flagship-forum-offers-stage-to-children-of-russian-elite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，弗拉基米尔·普京将他的家乡圣彼得堡变成了权力中心，举办了一场重要的经济活动。在俄罗斯前帝国首都举行的这次会议正日益成为克里姆林宫精英子女们的世代展示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/putin-s-flagship-forum-offers-stage-to-children-of-russian-elite</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士投票决定欧洲最高医疗成本 呼应美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/swiss-vote-on-europe-s-highest-health-costs-in-debate-echoing-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士人正准备投票决定是否要控制医疗体系的个人成本，该体系的收费比欧洲任何其他国家都要高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/swiss-vote-on-europe-s-highest-health-costs-in-debate-echoing-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国政府在冲突后寻求加强对央行的控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/thai-government-seeks-tighter-grip-on-central-bank-after-clash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维辛的政府正在讨论如何对泰国央行施加更多控制，此前该国央行在经济政策上多次与货币当局发生冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/thai-government-seeks-tighter-grip-on-central-bank-after-clash</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 03:47:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥总统加尔维斯要求选举机构重新计算 80% 的选票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/mexico-s-galvez-will-ask-electoral-body-to-recount-80-of-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥反对党领袖 Xochitl Galvez 表示，她将要求选举当局重新计算周日选举中 80% 的选票。在这场选举中，她输给了执政党候选人 Claudia Sheinbaum，失去了总统职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/mexico-s-galvez-will-ask-electoral-body-to-recount-80-of-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 03:12:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普拉博沃计划将水利机构作为印尼安全政策的一部分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/prabowo-plans-water-agency-as-part-of-indonesia-security-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，作为国家安全政策的一部分，印尼当选总统普拉博沃·苏比安托正计划成立一个新的政府机构，以解决该国长期存在的清洁水获取问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/prabowo-plans-water-agency-as-part-of-indonesia-security-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 02:54:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将缺席峰会 但仍将前往意大利和法国与泽连斯基会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/biden-to-meet-zelenskiy-in-italy-france-despite-skipping-summit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登计划在未来几周与乌克兰总统弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基举行两次会晤，尽管美国计划不参加即将在瑞士举行的和平峰会，但仍希望表达美国对基辅的声援。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/biden-to-meet-zelenskiy-in-italy-france-despite-skipping-summit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 01:44:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克在税收问题上抨击斯塔默，但在英国辩论中因受欢迎程度而落败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/sunak-hits-starmer-on-tax-but-loses-on-likability-in-uk-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 在英国首次与基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 进行竞选辩论时，使用了久经考验的保守党武器，反复警告工党领袖将提高税收。但他们在黄金时段的激烈电视辩论暴露了首相自己的弱点，也暴露了对手的弱点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/sunak-hits-starmer-on-tax-but-loses-on-likability-in-uk-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 00:43:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于以色列和哈马斯的反击，拜登结束加沙战争的努力受挫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/hamas-rejects-gaza-peace-plan-without-permanent-cease-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯跟随以色列，拒绝接受总统乔·拜登结束加沙战争的努力，双方都表示，必须满足各自提出的永久停火条件，他们才会同意停战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/hamas-rejects-gaza-peace-plan-without-permanent-cease-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 16:56:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安迪·金赢得新泽西州民主党参议院初选；共和党的蒂姆·希伊赢得蒙大拿州初选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-04/after-guilty-verdict-trump-will-appear-on-the-ballot-in-the-last-presidential-primaries-of-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约（美联社）——总统乔·拜登和前总统唐纳德·特朗普周二在几个州赢得了民主党和共和党初选，这是 2024 年初选日程中最后几场竞选之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-04/after-guilty-verdict-trump-will-appear-on-the-ballot-in-the-last-presidential-primaries-of-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 04:23:37 GMT</pubDate>
